    "This approach not only describes the real-time operation of actual elevators but also establishes a virtual connection to facilitate timely diagnosis of faults.",
    "Moreover, it can even proactively identify potential faults and anomalies before they occur.",
    "To summarize, the elevator digital twin model can not only improve the accuracy and efficient of elevator fault diagnosis, but also realize preventive maintenance, reduce maintenance cost, and improve the safety of elevators.",
